Instructions-Rc-car-Neo-pixel-1.0

You are working on a multi-file Arduino project.

Board:
Arduino Nano RP2040 Connect
Architecture: Arduino Mbed OS core (mbed_rp2040)

Scope restriction (very important):

Only read and analyze the files;
- 04_neo_pixel
- Adafruit_NeoPixel (copy 1)

Ignore all other files in the project.
All files except the NeoPixel module are read-only and out of scope.
Limit your reasoning to the NeoPixel module only.

Assume the rest of the project already works.

Task:
Work only on NeoPixel LED control.

Hardware:
WS2812 / NeoPixel strip
Pin 6
Using Adafruit_NeoPixel library compatible with RP2040 Mbed

Rules:
- Do not modify other files
- Do not suggest changes to other modules
- Only output code related to NeoPixel
- Show minimal changes only
- Do not rewrite the whole project

Code quality requirements:
- Make a comment for every function
- Each function comment must explain:
  - what the function does
  - why the function is needed
- Use clear embedded-style comments
- Keep code compatible with Mbed RP2040 core
- Avoid blocking delays
